requirements
To rent a golf cart, you must have a valid U.S. driver's license. Keystone Heights RV Resort will need a copy of the driver's license of each person planning to drive the golf cart.
​
You will also be required to fill out some paperwork before your rental.
​
If you have additional questions or concerns, you can reach us at
